    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CLEANING AXLE ASSEMBLIES</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">A complete axle can be steam-cleaned on the outside surface to remove dirt.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Before the axle is steam-cleaned, close or put a cover over all openings in the axle
                assembly. Examples of openings are breathers or vents in air chambers.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
